Without dropout.from sentence: Without dropout , the model overfits at around 300 epochs at 78 F1 .

Orthonormal parameter initialization.from sentence: Orthonormal parameter initialization is surprisingly important - without this , the model achieves only 65 F1 within the first 50 epochs .

8 layer ablations.from sentence: All 8 layer ablations suffer a loss of more than 1.7 in absolute F 1 compared to the full model .
